# Building RETRO on Linux

## Requirements

- c compiler (tested: clang, tcc, gcc)
- make
- standard unix shell

## Process

Run `make -f Makefile.linux`.

This will build the toolchain and then the main `retro`
executable.

## Executables

In the `bin/` directory:

    retro
    retro-unu
    retro-muri
    retro-extend
    retro-embedimage

